title: Meet Frances Tiafoe and Jack Sock
description: Tiafoe had plenty of big moments in the U.S. Open. And Sock has won four Grand Slam doubles titles.
dc:creator: Christopher Clarey
media:credit: Clive Brunskill/Getty Images For The Laver Cup
media:description: Frances Tiafoe, left, made waves during the U.S. Open. He is partnered with Jack Sock for the doubles match against Rafael Nadal and Roger Federer.
